data.description: Instant equity! This updated, one owner home is priced $35,000 under appraisal AND the seller is offering $20,000 in closing cost help! WOW! Updates include fresh paint inside and out, new flooring, new appliances, new AC, new fence, and a brand new roof...there is nothing left for you to do except move in! With two spacious living areas, four bedrooms, and three full bathrooms the open concept living space allows plenty of room for entertaining family and friends. The large lot it sits on (.281 of an acre) provides a generous area outdoors as well. Come see this fantastic home in Lubbock-Cooper school district!
